{"type": "article", "id": 16414, "title": "Gentle Hint chairs", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-22T07:01:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000341iDn79dVlZJ3kpvtr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t哈萨克族设计师 Nissa Kinzhalina 设计了这两把金属椅子，看似用一个连贯的结构做椅子的支撑和靠背。方形的黑色座位与金属支撑的厚度一致，从侧面看过去，椅子就像只有一根线条，但当视线与座位齐平时，又像只有一些独立的框架。设计师曾在日本的工作室学习，这组椅子也是日式极简的诠释。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143704Xp8DFHxj5YJAsZrS.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143704TraW8opE35HywGmt.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"937\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00106838\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143705sAWg79p4UvCjOLGf.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"935\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261437054lhPaZCTO5wRyveJ.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1088\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.16239316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}